thread.title: Russell Stevenson

author: Russell Stevenson
title: Russell Stevenson
text: I had done research about finding the correct look and feel for an office that would match myself and my brand. I looked at others and they just didn't have the feel and the match I needed. I then met with Alice and Taylor at Servcorp Docklands and I knew straight away it was a perfect fit. The location, the style, the professionalism and the presentation of the building, the office and the Servcorp team matched myself and my brand perfectly. It's only been a short time since I moved in but I have no hesitation in recommending Servcorp Docklands and the Servcorp Docklands Team.
